Package: fixsvg
Title: Fix SVG files that are affected by the Firefox bug
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Francois", "Michonneau", role=c("aut", "cre"),
                                email="francois.michonneau@gmail.com")
Description: Some versions of Firefox have a bug that affects the display of SVG file that contain the 'clip-path' element. This package contains a function that automatically remove this element.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
  purrr,
  xml2
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
URL: https://github.com/fmichonneau/fixsvg
BugReports: https://github.com/fmichonneau/fixsvg/issues
